            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>快扣(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:FAST:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/FAST\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">FAST-US</a>)截至台北時間06日00:07股價下跌2.52美元，報47.76美元，跌幅5%，成交量3,931,700（股），盤中最高價49.36美元、最低價47.75美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.49%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.41%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.33%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+1.05%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>快扣(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:FAST:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/FAST\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">FAST-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+0.18%</li> <li>近 1 月：+10.8%</li> <li>近 3 月：+22.97%</li> <li>近 6 月：-32.28%</li> <li>今年以來：-30.09%</li></ul></section></main>",
